snippet.title: Operation STEEL Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1489300/Operation_STEEL/

A Roguelike Shoot-em-up with beautiful hand-painted art, unique enemies and loads of random weapons and items to take them down with!

Join the Discord for more info: https://discord.gg/6HzPrPt
